request.description:
Get main dashboard showing key metrics across all prodi in the faculty.

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "total_mahasiswa": 450,
    "distribusi_status": { "MERAH": 12, "KUNING": 35, "HIJAU": 300, "BIRU": 103 },
    "mahasiswa_bahaya": 12,
    "mahasiswa_issues": 47
  }
}
```

Trigger EWS status recalculation for all students across all prodi.

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Recalculation started",
  "data": { "total_diproses": 450, "status_berubah": 8 }
}
```

Get top 10 most failed courses across all prodi.

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    { "mk_id": 1, "kode_mk": "A11.54321", "nama_mk": "Struktur Data", "jumlah_gagal": 25 }
  ]
}
```

Get academic achievement summary cards.

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "rata_ips": 3.55,
    "jumlah_mahasiswa_at_risk": 47,
    "persentase_lulus_tepat_waktu": 78.5,
    "total_matkul_gagal": 120
  }
}
```

